          <h1 class="probh1">Problem Statement</h1>
          <br />
          <!--       <p class = "probp"> We will be releasing problem statement very soon. Stay in touch. </p> -->
          <p class="probp">
            Loss of biodiversity is an unattended pressing issue. The current
            action plan is not able to handle the problem effectively. We, at
            MEGALITH, expect the prospective participants to suggest some new
            feasible solutions to overcome the increasing loss of biodiversity
            and thereby ensure sustainable development.<br /><br />
            Note:<br /><br />
            1. Presentation with Unique and relevant solutions will be
            prioritized over others<br /><br />
            2. The presentation must include answers to all the questions in the
            PS.<br /><br />
            3. Teams will also be judged on basis of the Involvement of all the
            participants of the team, way of presentation, and time limit.
          </p>
          <br />
        </div>
      </div>

