          <h1 class="ruleh1">Rules</h1>
          <br />
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ Teams must consist of a minimum of 2 and a maximum of 5
            participants.
          </p>
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ The team must consist of at least one member from the Department of
            Civil Engineering.
          </p>
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ The event will be conducted in two phases: a. Online submission of
            abstract b. Final presentation by shortlisted teams at IIT Kharagpur
          </p>
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ Shortlisted teams from the abstract submission round have to
            present their ideas in the form of PowerPoint presentations during
            Megalith 2023 at IIT Kharagpur.
          </p>
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ The abstract should be submitted with a minimum font size of 11
            and single line spacing and must not exceed 3 pages.
          </p>

          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ The abstract should be supported with valid references.
          </p>

          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ Relevant statistics can be added to support your claim (you may
            add one extra page to include stats, and images and hyperlink them
            wherever required).
          </p>

          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ Time limit for the final presentation is 10 minutes.
          </p>
          <p class="rulep">
            ❖ The decision of judges shall be final and binding.
          </p>
